response.overview: April 14th, 2012 :: Combat Zone Wrestling presents Best Of The Best 11 from the Flyers Skate Zone from Voorhees Township, NJ, USA. The show featured the Best Of The Best tournament. Matches include:  • 1st Round Elimination Match Drake Younger vs. Sami Callihan vs. MK McKinnan vs. Trent Seven  • 1st Round Elimination Match Greg Excellent vs. Alex Colon (w/Chrissy Rivera) vs. Willie Mack  • 1st Round Elimination Match Chuck Taylor vs. Johnny Gargano vs. Samuray del Sol  • 1st Round Elimination Match Lince Dorado vs. AR Fox vs. ACH  • CZW Wired TV Title Match Jake Crist (c) vs. Dave Crist  • Best Of The Best 11 Semi Final Matches  • Ultraviolent Match Matt Tremont vs. Clint Margera (w/DJ Hyde)  • Best Of The Best 11 Final Match
response.title: CZW Best Of The Best 11
